Package project2

Class Student

java.lang.Object
project2.Student
Direct Known Subclasses:
NonResident, Resident
public class Student
extends Object
The Student Super class is where we create a student of type Student. There are getter and setter methods for the Student's properties (except class). Two subclass extend student.
Author:
Manav Bali, Daniel Lopez
